    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>The example HTMLBox with defined Url property value as http://visualwebgui.com/. You can change URL in 'URL' Textbox and content of HTMLBox will be changed.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui HtmlBox control contains Url property that defines URL of the HTML pages.</p>]]></Paragraph>
